@BoardVerse.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5022

### Health
GET {{BoardVerse.API_HostAddress}}/api/health/ping

### Board Games — categories (filter UI)
GET {{BoardVerse.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/board-games/categories

### Board Games — search + filter
GET {{BoardVerse.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/board-games?search=ma%20soi&player_count=6&duration_range=ThirtyToSixty

### Board Games — detail by id
GET {{BoardVerse.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/board-games/66666666-6666-6666-6666-666666666666

### Board Games — detail (explicit path)
GET {{BoardVerse.API_HostAddress}}/api/v1/board-games/66666666-6666-6666-6666-666666666666/details

### Cafe inventory — public browse (with description, categories, components)
GET {{BoardVerse.API_HostAddress}}/api/cafes/bbbbbbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbb-bbbbbbbbbbbb/inventory?searchTerm=catan
